{"comments":"Keyframe Toggle (Stopwatch) Component\n\nThe iconic stopwatch button used in After Effects to enable/disable\nanimation on a property. When active, the property can be keyframed.\n\n## Visual States\n\n```\n  ◇  Inactive (no keyframes, hollow diamond)\n  ◆  Active (has keyframes, filled diamond)\n  ⏱  At keyframe (current time has a keyframe)\n```\n\n## Features\n\n- Click to toggle animation enable/disable\n- Alt+click to add keyframe at current time\n- Visual distinction for active/inactive states\n- Shows when current time is at a keyframe\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Component.Motion.Property.KeyframeToggle as KeyframeToggle\n\nHH.slot _toggle unit KeyframeToggle.component\n  { isAnimated: true\n  , hasKeyframeAtCurrentTime: false\n  , disabled: false\n  }\n  HandleToggleOutput\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"KeyframeToggle component\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"m","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"constraintAnn":[],"constraintArgs":[{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"constraintClass":[["Effect","Aff","Class"],"MonadAff"],"constraintData":null,"constraintKindArgs":[]},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Halogen","Component"],"Component"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Property","KeyframeToggle"],"Query"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Property","KeyframeToggle"],"Input"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Component","Motion","Property","KeyframeToggle"],"Output"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"m","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"ConstrainedType"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvisible"},"t